      <h1 class="bc-analitics__h1">Индексы</h1>
      <div class="d-flex justify-content-center justify-content-md-start mt-4 mb-5">
        <a class="bc-article__btn-xs-w-100 btn btn-dark d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" href="https://bloomchain-cdn.s3.amazonaws.com/uploads/pdf/7a93be6a-afeb-11ea-9b8e-0242ac130004/Индексы_методология_корр.pdf?v=63759542850" target="_blank">Скачать Методику</a>
